Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:29.17,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}そしていま　ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:34.43,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}それぞれの道を　見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:39.70,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}そしていま　また歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:45.51,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}ふたつの想いが　めぐり会う　その日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:49.63,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}迷いながらも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:54.49,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}夢の色重ねる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:57.66,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}君を想うからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:22:00.23,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}強くなれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:01.48,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.96,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}終わらせない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:10.11,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}そしていま　私は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:15.17,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}輝く明日を　見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:20.86,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}そしていま　ほら響くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:28.26,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}君が教えてくれた歌　この空に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:29.17,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}现在 我们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:34.43,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}凝视着各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:39.70,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}如今 我仍在歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:45.51,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}直至两份心意再次交融
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:49.63,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}纵使迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:54.49,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}仍追忆梦想之色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:57.66,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}正因思念你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:22:00.23,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}我才能坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:01.48,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}我一定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.96,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}不会就此停步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:10.11,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}现在 我们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:15.17,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}凝望着那光彩夺目的明日
